OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA dry and bright morning and
OL,6,Fbecoming hot again inland, though
OL,7,Fsunshine turning hazy at times. Cloud
OL,8,Fincreasing through the afternoon with
OL,9,Fsome heavy showers developing.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FCloudy with outbreaks of
OL,12,Frain, these heavy and thundery at
OL,13,Ftimes. Rain becomes more confined to
OL,14,Fthe north and east towards morning.
OL,15,
OL,16,CSaturday:FAny overnight heavy rain
OL,17,Fsoon clearing in the morning.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
